
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Credix - Empréstimos</title>
    <%- include('partials/favicon') %>
    <%- include('partials/toast') %>
    <%- include('partials/session-timeout') %>
    <style>
        html, body { background-color: #020617; }
</style>
    <script>
        (function () {
            const root = document.documentElement;
            try {
                const savedTheme = localStorage.getItem('theme');
                if (savedTheme === 'dark') root.classList.add('dark');
                if (savedTheme === 'light') root.classList.remove('dark');
            } catch (error) {}
        })();

        window.tailwind = window.tailwind || {};
        window.tailwind.config = Object.assign({}, window.tailwind.config || {}, { darkMode: 'class' });
    </script>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        html { font-size: 16px; }
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; overflow-x: hidden; }

        .primary-gradient { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000000 0%, #0f172a 50%, #111827 100%); }
        .premium-header { background: rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.75); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.2); }

        .icon-btn {
            color: #cbd5e1;
            width: 42px;
            height: 42px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            transition: background-color 120ms ease-out, color 120ms ease-out, box-shadow 120ms ease-out;
        }
        .icon-btn:hover {
            color: #ffffff;
            background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.35) inset;
        }

        .modern-sidebar {
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.9) 0%, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.85) 100%);
            border-right: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.18);
            transform: translateX(0);
            transition: transform 120ms ease-out;
        }
        .sidebar-item {
            transition: background-color 120ms ease-out, color 120ms ease-out, box-shadow 120ms ease-out;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 4px 0;
        }
        .sidebar-item:hover {
            background: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.12);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.2) inset;
        }
        .sidebar-item.active {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e40af 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(147, 197, 253, 0.5) inset, 0 2px 8px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.25);
        }

        .glass-card {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
        }
        .page-title { color: #ffffff; }
        .muted-on-dark { color: #cbd5e1; }

        .kpi-label {
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        }
        .kpi-value {
            color: #0f172a;
            font-size: 1.375rem;
            line-height: 1.05;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .kpi-insight {
            margin-top: 6px;
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #64748b;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }
        .kpi-insight-positive { color: #047857; }
        .kpi-insight-negative { color: #b91c1c; }
        .filter-control {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            color: #111827;
            width: 100%;
        }
        #loanModal .filter-control:focus,
        #loanModal button:focus,
        #loanSearch:focus,
        #loanStatusFilter:focus {
            outline: none !important;
            box-shadow: none !important;
        }
        .filter-control.field-invalid {
            border-color: #ef4444;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
        }
        .field-error {
            margin-top: 6px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #dc2626;
            display: none;
        }
        .field-error:not(:empty) { display: block; }

        .table-shell {
            overflow: auto;
            border-radius: 14px;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            background: #f8fafc;
        }
        .table-shell table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
        .table-shell th {
            text-align: left;
            background: #f8fafc;
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
            padding: 12px 14px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        .table-shell td { padding: 16px 14px; border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9; color: #1f2937; }

        .badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 2px 10px;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .badge-success { background: #dcfce7; color: #166534; }
        .badge-danger { background: #fee2e2; color: #991b1b; }
        .badge-warn { background: #fef3c7; color: #92400e; }
        .badge-neutral { background: #e2e8f0; color: #334155; }

        .action-btn {
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border: 1px solid transparent;
            transition: background-color 120ms ease-out, border-color 120ms ease-out;
        }
        .action-btn-view { color: #2563eb; }
        .action-btn-edit { color: #059669; }
        .action-btn-delete { color: #dc2626; }
        .action-btn-view:hover,
        .action-btn-edit:hover,
        .action-btn-delete:hover {
            background: #f1f5f9;
            border-color: #e2e8f0;
        }

        .calc-card {
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.25);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(30, 64, 175, 0.08) 0%, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.12) 100%);
            box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
        }

        .loan-action-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            padding-top: 0.5rem;
        }

        .loan-btn-secondary {
            border-color: #b7c9ea;
            background: #eef4ff;
            color: #28446f;
        }

        .loan-btn-secondary:hover {
            background: #e2ecfb;
            border-color: #9fb5d8;
            color: #1f3a61;
        }

        .loan-btn-primary {
            border: 1px solid #9fb5d8;
            background: #c9d8ee;
            color: #163a66;
        }

        .loan-btn-primary:hover {
            background: #bccfe8;
            border-color: #8ea8d0;
            color: #122f55;
        }
        .installment-preview {
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            background: #f8fafc;
        }
        .installment-preview.overdue { background: #fee2e2; border-color: #fecaca; }
        .installment-preview.pending { background: #fef3c7; border-color: #fde68a; }
        .installment-preview.overdue:hover { background: #fecaca; }
        .installment-preview.pending:hover { background: #fde68a; }

        .details-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 12px;
        }
        .details-item {
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            background: #f8fafc;
        }

        main { transition: none; }
        body.sidebar-collapsed .modern-sidebar { transform: translateX(-100%); }
        body.sidebar-collapsed main { margin-left: 0 !important; }

        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .modern-sidebar { transform: translateX(-100%); }
            .modern-sidebar.mobile-open { transform: translateX(0) !important; }
            main { margin-left: 0 !important; }
            main { width: 100% !important; flex: 1 1 100% !important; }
        }
        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .kpi-value { font-size: 1.3rem; }
            .details-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(1, minmax(0, 1fr)); }

            .icon-btn {
                width: 36px;
                height: 36px;
                border-radius: 10px;
            }

            .icon-btn i {
                font-size: 1rem !important;
            }

            .header-user-chevron { display: none; }

            #userMenuBtn {
                max-width: min(46vw, 11rem);
                justify-content: flex-end;
            }

            .header-user-name {
                display: inline-block;
                max-width: 100%;
                overflow: hidden;
                text-overflow: ellipsis;
                white-space: nowrap;
            }
        }

        .dark .glass-card {
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.82);
            border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.2);
            color: #e2e8f0;
            box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.35);
        }
        .dark .kpi-value { color: #f8fafc; }
        .dark .kpi-insight { color: #cbd5e1; }
        .dark .kpi-insight-positive { color: #86efac; }
        .dark .kpi-insight-negative { color: #fca5a5; }
        .dark .filter-control,
        .dark .table-shell,
        .dark .table-shell th,
        .dark .table-shell td,
        .dark .details-item,
        .dark .installment-preview {
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.7);
            color: #e2e8f0;
            border-color: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.22);
        }
        .dark .field-error { color: #fca5a5; }
        .dark .table-shell th { background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.95); color: #cbd5e1; }
        .dark .calc-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(30, 64, 175, 0.2) 0%, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.22) 100%);
            border-color: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.35);
            box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(2, 6, 23, 0.35);
        }

        .dark .loan-btn-secondary {
            border-color: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.45);
            background: rgba(51, 65, 85, 0.55);
            color: #e2e8f0;
        }

        .dark .loan-btn-secondary:hover {
            background: rgba(71, 85, 105, 0.6);
            border-color: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.55);
            color: #f8fafc;
        }

        .dark .loan-btn-primary {
            border-color: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.5);
            background: rgba(30, 64, 175, 0.38);
            color: #dbeafe;
        }

        .dark .loan-btn-primary:hover {
            background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.44);
            border-color: rgba(147, 197, 253, 0.55);
            color: #eff6ff;
        }
        /* Premium DS v1 - light skin */
        :root {
            --premium-bg: #121b2a;
            --premium-sidebar: #13203a;
            --premium-card: #E3E9F2;
            --premium-positive: #16A34A;
            --premium-negative: #DC2626;
            --premium-accent: #1E40AF;
            --premium-radius: 16px;
            --premium-shadow-soft: 0 4px 12px rgba(2, 12, 27, 0.08);
        }

        html, body {
            background-color: var(--premium-bg);
        }

        .primary-gradient {
            background:
                radial-gradient(900px 320px at -10% -10%, rgba(30, 64, 175, 0.18), transparent 60%),
                var(--premium-bg);
        }

        .premium-header {
            background: rgba(18, 27, 42, 0.88);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.24);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
        }

        .modern-sidebar {
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #15253f 0%, var(--premium-sidebar) 100%);
            border-right: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.2);
        }

        .sidebar-item.active {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1B3D8F 0%, #234EA8 100%);
        }

        .glass-card,
        .kpi-card,
        .summary-link,
        .modal-panel,
        .modal-content {
            background: var(--premium-card);
            border-radius: var(--premium-radius);
            border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.28);
            box-shadow: var(--premium-shadow-soft);
        }

        .rounded-2xl {
            border-radius: var(--premium-radius);
        }

        .badge,
        .status-pill {
            border-radius: 999px;
            font-weight: 700;
            border: 1px solid transparent;
        }

        .badge-success,
        .status-green {
            background: rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.14);
            color: var(--premium-positive);
            border-color: rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.34);
        }

        .badge-danger,
        .status-red {
            background: rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.12);
            color: var(--premium-negative);
            border-color: rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.36);
        }

        .badge-warn,
        .status-yellow {
            background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.16);
            color: #b45309;
            border-color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.35);
        }

        .app-toast {
            position: fixed;
            top: 1rem;
            left: 1rem;
            right: 1rem;
            z-index: 60;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            max-width: 420px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.42);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(5, 85, 70, 0.9) 0%, rgba(3, 55, 48, 0.95) 100%);
            color: #d1fae5;
            padding: 12px 14px;
            font-size: 0.98rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            line-height: 1.25;
            box-shadow: 0 16px 38px -22px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.75), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(167, 243, 208, 0.16);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            transition: opacity 200ms ease, transform 200ms ease;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .app-toast.show {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        .app-toast-error {
            border-color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.42);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(127, 29, 29, 0.92) 0%, rgba(69, 10, 10, 0.95) 100%);
            color: #fee2e2;
            box-shadow: 0 16px 38px -22px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.7), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(254, 202, 202, 0.15);
        }

        .app-toast-icon {
            width: 34px;
            height: 34px;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.22);
            color: #a7f3d0;
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.35);
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .app-toast-error .app-toast-icon {
            background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.22);
            color: #fecaca;
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.35);
        }

        .app-toast-text {
            word-break: break-word;
        }

        @media (min-width: 640px) {
            .app-toast {
                left: auto;
                top: 1.5rem;
                right: 1.5rem;
            }
        }

        .notification-badge,
        .btn-primary,
        .action-primary {
            background: var(--premium-accent);
        }
        html:not(.dark) main .bg-white { background-color: #e3e9f2 !important; }
        html:not(.dark) main .bg-slate-50 { background-color: #d9e1ec !important; }
        html:not(.dark) main .border-gray-200,
        html:not(.dark) main .border-gray-300,
        html:not(.dark) main .border-slate-200,
        html:not(.dark) main .border-slate-300 { border-color: #c6d0df !important; }
        html:not(.dark) main .hover\\:bg-gray-50:hover,
        html:not(.dark) main .hover\\:bg-slate-50:hover { background-color: #d3ddea !important; }

        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .loan-action-row {
                flex-direction: column-reverse;
                align-items: stretch;
                gap: 0.5rem;
            }

            .loan-action-row > button {
                width: 100%;
            }
        }
</style>
</head>
<body class="primary-gradient min-h-screen">
    <header class="premium-header fixed w-full top-0 z-50">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between px-3 py-3 sm:px-6 sm:py-4">
            <div class="flex items-center">
                <button id="sidebarToggle" class="icon-btn focus:outline-none"><i class="fas fa-bars text-xl"></i></button>
                <h1 class="ml-3 sm:ml-6">
                    <a href="dashboard.html" class="flex items-center" aria-label="Credix">
                        <%- include('partials/brand-wordmark', { size: 'header' }) %>
                    </a>
                </h1>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-1 items-center justify-end gap-1 sm:gap-4 lg:gap-6 min-w-0">
                <div class="relative min-w-0">
                    <button id="userMenuBtn" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-200 hover:text-white focus:outline-none min-w-0 max-w-full overflow-hidden">
                        <span id="userName" class="header-user-name font-semibold min-w-0 truncate">Olá, <%= currentUser?.name || currentUser?.full_name || 'Administrador' %></span>
                        <i class="header-user-chevron fas fa-chevron-down text-sm"></i>
                    </button>
                    <div id="userMenuDropdown" class="absolute right-0 top-full z-50 mt-2 hidden w-56 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-2 shadow-xl dark:border-slate-700 dark:bg-slate-900">
                        <button type="button" data-user-menu-action="profile" class="flex w-full items-center gap-2 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-100 dark:text-slate-200 dark:hover:bg-slate-800">
                            <i class="fas fa-id-card text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-300"></i>
                            <span>Meu perfil</span>
                        </button>
                        <button type="button" data-user-menu-action="security" class="flex w-full items-center gap-2 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-100 dark:text-slate-200 dark:hover:bg-slate-800">
                            <i class="fas fa-shield-halved text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-300"></i>
                            <span>Segurança</span>
                        </button>
                        <button type="button" data-user-menu-action="help" class="flex w-full items-center gap-2 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-100 dark:text-slate-200 dark:hover:bg-slate-800">
                            <i class="fas fa-circle-question text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-300"></i>
                            <span>Ajuda</span>
                        </button>
                        <div class="my-1 h-px bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700"></div>
                        <button type="button" data-user-menu-action="logout" class="flex w-full items-center gap-2 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-red-600 hover:bg-red-50 dark:text-red-400 dark:hover:bg-red-950/40">
                            <i class="fas fa-right-from-bracket"></i>
                            <span>Sair</span>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="flex pt-16 sm:pt-20">
        <aside id="sidebar" class="modern-sidebar fixed left-0 top-16 h-[calc(100%-4rem)] w-64 z-40 sm:top-20 sm:h-[calc(100%-5rem)]">
            <nav class="mt-8 px-4">
                <ul class="space-y-2">
                    <li><a href="dashboard.html" class="sidebar-item flex items-center px-4 py-3 text-gray-300 hover:text-white rounded-lg"><i class="fas fa-tachometer-alt mr-4 text-lg"></i><span>Painel financeiro</span></a></li>
                    <li><a href="debtors.html" class="sidebar-item flex items-center px-4 py-3 text-gray-300 hover:text-white rounded-lg"><i class="fas fa-users mr-4 text-lg"></i><span>Clientes</span></a></li>
                    <li><a href="loans.html" class="sidebar-item active flex items-center px-4 py-3 text-white rounded-lg"><i class="fas fa-hand-holding-usd mr-4 text-lg"></i><span class="font-medium">Empréstimos</span></a></li>
                    <li><a href="installments.html" class="sidebar-item flex items-center px-4 py-3 text-gray-300 hover:text-white rounded-lg"><i class="fas fa-calendar-check mr-4 text-lg"></i><span>Parcelas</span></a></li>
                    <li><a href="reports.html" class="sidebar-item flex items-center px-4 py-3 text-gray-300 hover:text-white rounded-lg"><i class="fas fa-chart-bar mr-4 text-lg"></i><span>Relatórios</span></a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </aside>

        <main class="flex-1 ml-64 p-4 sm:p-6 lg:p-8">
            <div class="mb-6 flex flex-col gap-4 md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="page-title text-3xl font-bold">Empréstimos</h2>
                    <p class="muted-on-dark mt-1 text-sm">Acompanhe contratos, valores e status da carteira ativa.</p>
                </div>
                <button id="newLoanBtn" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-blue-600 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition-colors duration-150 hover:bg-blue-500">
                    <i class="fas fa-file-invoice-dollar mr-2"></i>Novo empréstimo
                </button>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-5 mb-6">
                <div class="relative rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-5 shadow-sm">
                    <span class="pointer-events-none absolute right-4 top-4 text-slate-400/80"><i class="fas fa-hashtag"></i></span>
                    <p class="kpi-label">Qtd. empréstimos</p>
                    <p id="totalLoans" class="kpi-value mt-3">0</p>
                    <p id="totalLoansInsight" class="kpi-insight">--</p>
                </div>
                <div class="relative rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-5 shadow-sm">
                    <span class="pointer-events-none absolute right-4 top-4 text-slate-400/80"><i class="fas fa-hand-holding-usd"></i></span>
                    <p class="kpi-label">Principal total</p>
                    <p id="totalPrincipal" class="kpi-value mt-3">R$ 0,00</p>
                    <p id="totalPrincipalInsight" class="kpi-insight">--</p>
                </div>
                <div class="relative rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-5 shadow-sm">
                    <span class="pointer-events-none absolute right-4 top-4 text-slate-400/80"><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i></span>
                    <p class="kpi-label">Total contratado</p>
                    <p id="totalContracted" class="kpi-value mt-3">R$ 0,00</p>
                    <p id="totalContractedInsight" class="kpi-insight">--</p>
                </div>
                <div class="relative rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-5 shadow-sm">
